  <brief_title>AVE8062 in Combination With Platinum-taxane Doublet in Advanced Solid Tumor</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Open-label, Non-randomized, Dose Evaluation, Safety and Pharmacokinetics Phase I Study of AVE8062 in Combination With Platinum Salts (Cisplatin or Carboplatin) and Taxanes (Docetaxel or Paclitaxel), Every 3 Weeks, in Patients With Advanced Solid Tumors.</official_title>
